Looking for where to buy the right thing from a mobile phone or tablet at low prices? You no longer need to visit 100,500 different websites, download various applications of online stores, look for very profitable offers and discounts, because all this is collected in our “Umka Mall” program. The world of shopping to order is open on your gadget!

Characteristics of the application “Umka Mall”

Together with our trading application, you can buy the right product at low prices. Our program is a mobile online store where you can find and view the necessary things in the catalog, analyze other users' requests, choose the cheapest delivery option and make an online purchase and track the delivery.

Features of the program:

1. With our application, you can specify the desired product, and the program itself will select recommendations for you. So you can compare several options from the catalog and buy the best of them to order.
2. We have created for you a convenient filtering system, so you can search using filters and categories.
3. Liked some product, look at it and want to postpone “for later”, do not buy now? Then add it to your favorites list
4. Want to share with friends and family your favorite option? Send them a link via VK, Facebook, Instagram, Telegram and other convenient applications.

Our customers order both wholesale and retail goods from China or from real boutiques, and spend less than an hour on the checkout process.

The advantages of the online store “Umka Mall”

With the help of our program for mobile, you can choose and buy the best products:

● electronics and home appliances for the home;
● cheap men's or women's clothing and shoes, bags and accessories;
● mobile phones and additions to them, following the example of covers;
● products for children and their parents;
● Chinese or European instruments;
● computer equipment;
● garden furniture;
● all for outdoor recreation;
● products for a hobby;
● cosmetics and health products;
● spare parts for vehicles and motorcycles, as well as other things and toys.

In addition, we provide our customers with free mail delivery services in Russia, Belarus, Ukraine, Kazakhstan and other CIS countries and the world. Our products are sold from Russia and various foreign warehouses, therefore delivery times may vary: for Moscow from 1 to 5 days, areas from 1 to 5 days, St. Petersburg: from 5 to 8 days, other regions of Russia: from 1 to 30 days

With us you can not be afraid about the quality of the product, because we make sure that the ratio of price and quality always remains at the level, be it electronics, cheap men's or women's clothing, household appliances, dresses or other items from the catalog. Have questions when choosing? Not a problem, in our application there is technical support for customers in Russian. The application itself is available in Russian and English.

Warranty conditions and return of goods in the online hypermarket “Umka Mall”

Each purchase in the online online store is protected:

1. Your personal information and contact details remain secure, not distributed.
2. You can order a position and pay by credit card, Yandex Money, Paypal. If within 24 hours the goods have not been sent, the program will offer to cancel the order and return the funds.
3. Also available to you after-sales service and logistic protection. If within 60 days of the payment, the goods did not arrive by mail, we will refund your money.

And if the purchases do not come up, you can return them within 30 days of receipt, having first submitted the application. If the product is damaged or does not match the description, take a photo or video for us as proof, we will process them within 7 days, and if we confirm the discrepancy, we will refund or exchange the order.

E-mail us or call: support@umkamall.ru and + 7-812-317-74-30. The customer service is open from Monday to Friday from 9:00 to 18:00, excluding official holidays.

